Large event barn, Farmhouse event space & 2 bridal suites
Windmill wedding alter, outdoor stage & seating, outdoor volleyball courts, grain bin bar & horshoe pit
Minutes from Lake Okoboji in Northwest Iowa, The Barn at Okoboji sits on 15 acres of peaceful farm land with ample parking and room to expand

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The Barn at Okoboji is an event center & restaurant built around a century old barn on 15 acres in Spirit Lake, Iowa.  The multi-faced farm is 7,500 square feet of rustic charm and host a wide range of events including weddings, corporate gatherings, concerts and parties of all sizes.
